+  class  size almost_full almost_empty obj_allocated   obj_used pages_used pages_per_zspage freeable
+  ...
+    202  3264           0            0             0          0          0                4        0
+    206  3328           0            0             0          0          0               13        0
+    207  3344           0            0             0          0          0                9        0
+    208  3360           0            0             0          0          0               14        0
