+config ZSMALLOC_CHAIN_SIZE
+	int "Maximum number of physical pages per-zspage"
+	default 8
+	range 4 16
+	depends on ZSMALLOC
+	help
+	  This option sets the upper limit on the number of physical pages
+	  that a zmalloc page (zspage) can consist of. The optimal zspage
